-``nid`` is optionally required for only ``node_mem_used_bp``,
-``node_mem_free_bp``, ``node_memcg_used_bp`` and ``node_memcg_free_bp`` to
+``nid`` is optionally required for ``node_mem_used_bp``, ``node_mem_free_bp``,
